# Phase 85a Linux Packaging Spike — .gitignore
#
# Excludes build artifacts and per-run logs from version control. The build
# pipeline lives IN build.sh / verify-pins.sh (committed); their outputs do not.

# Build artifact tree (linuxdeploy outputs live here)
artifacts/

# AppImage outputs (large binary, regenerable from build.sh)
*.AppImage

# AppDir staging trees (intermediate; mksquashfs source)
*.AppDir/

# Per-run logs (captured into findings doc when relevant, but raw logs are regenerable)
build.log
smoke.log

# Per-distro evidence artifacts (originals embedded in 85A-SPIKE-FINDINGS.md)
*-screenshot.png
*-transcript.log

# Plan 03 pin-verification lock file (regenerable from verify-pins.sh; the pin
# SOURCE lives in build.sh as SHA256 constants — only the verification artifact
# is gitignored)
verify-pins.lock
